  'You are appraising the property at 2234 Ridge View Terrace, Landrum, SC 29356 for a conventional residential purchase loan. The subject is 3BR/2BA · 1,680 SF · 2001-built SFR · Blue Ridge Estates. Section 5 — Locational Influence — requires you to identify which locational factors are present at the subject, classify each present factor as Positive, Negative, Neutral, or Market-Dependent based on the location profile evidence, and write a brief market-supported rationale for each classification. Distractor factors that are not present at this location must be left unchecked. Every classification must be grounded in specific evidence from the location profile — this assignment evaluates evidence-based locational analysis, not pattern recognition or reflexive checklist behavior.'
